3) Ground item drops
- [x] Drop monster loot to world tiles instead of direct inventory award.
- [x] Drop player-discarded items to world tiles instead of deleting.
- [x] Add ground-item pickup interaction and inventory-capacity handling.
- [x] Add ownership visibility window: only owner sees item for first 60s.
- [x] Open visibility to all players after 60s if still on ground.
- [x] Despawn ground items after 120s total lifetime.

4) Map Making
- [x] Add browser-based map editor page with paint-like placement workflow.
- [x] Add tile palette (grass/sand/water/etc.) and brush placement tools.
- [x] Add placement palettes for monsters and resources.
- [x] Add erase tool and simple undo/redo actions.
- [x] Add select tool for tile/entity inspection.
- [x] Add save/load for map data to JSON files.
- [x] Add chunk coordinate workflow with per-chunk load/export.

5) Player login + account security
- [ ] Add account registration/login (email or username + password).
- [ ] Store passwords with salted hash (Argon2/bcrypt), never plain text.
- [ ] Add signed session/auth token flow with server-side validation.
- [ ] Bind profile saves/loads to authenticated account IDs only.
- [ ] Add basic anti-tamper controls (request validation + rate limiting).

6) Quest / task loop
- [ ] Add basic kill tasks.
- [ ] Add basic gather tasks.
- [ ] Add coin/xp/gear reward hooks.

7) Economy balancing
- [ ] Re-tune buy/sell pricing curves.
- [ ] Add at least one coin sink (repair, fees, etc.).
- [ ] Add economy telemetry counters for tuning.

8) Save/profile hardening
- [ ] Add profile schema version field.
- [ ] Add migration pipeline for old profiles.
- [ ] Add migration safety/fallback logging.

